> FYI, if they do a 
> 	bk send -ubk://linux.bkbits.net/linux-2.5 torvalds@transmeta.com
> that problem goes away.  The -u<url> stuff does the same sort of
> handshake that a pull does to figure out what needs to be sent to fill
